  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Ni qolqewan nitaj qoriwan rantikorqa almayqa./
 /Jesuspa yawamillanwanmin, ancha jatun preciowan./
 
[V2]
 /Ruwasqasniywanqa nipuni salvakúy atiymanchu,
 /Manachay Jesús sapallampi creesqayrayku sonqowaix/
 
</lyrics></song>